title: The FoodSaver® FM1510 Fresh Food Preservation System - Containers
description: The FoodSaver Fresh Food Preservation System seals in freshness of foods stored in the fridge, pantry and on the go. Easily and conveniently vacuum seal FoodSaver Fresh Containers and Vacuum Zipper Bags for storage of everyday foods, leftovers and prep-ahead ingredients. Its compact design is made for everyday countertop use and its one-touch sealing allows for hand-free operation once the sealing process starts.

Easily and conveniently vacuum seal FoodSaver® Fresh Containers and Vacuum Zipper Bags for storage of everyday foods, leftovers and prep-ahead ingredients. transcripts: It's easy to extend the freshness of your food with the FoodSaver fresh food preservation system and its specially designed to work with your food saver fresh containers so you can keep your food fresh up to two times longer than ordinary food storage. To get started place your fresh container onto the base of the appliance platform press the buttons to adjust the height of the vacuum head firmly press the vacuum port on to the container valve just press start and it does the rest, the vacuum process stops automatically when freshness is sealed in. Perfect for storing your favorite foods in the fridge or the pantry or to take on the go. Trust your food freshness to the new foodsaver fresh food preservation system.
